data.description: Welcome to this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence built in 2003. Located in a serene neighborhood, this house offers a modern and comfortable living space. The master bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom, while two additional bedrooms share a second bathroom featuring a convenient shower, sink, and toilet.  The well-maintained property boasts a spacious living area, a functional kitchen for all your culinary needs, and a designated dining area for family gatherings or entertaining guests. You'll find the backyard perfect for relaxation and outdoor activities.  This home is not just a place to live but a place to create lasting memories. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
